# Design & Brand

## Theme

Dark-only site. `Providers` forces `dark` theme — do not add light-mode variants unless explicitly requested.

## Color Palette

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Background | `#0a0a0f` | Page base (`globals.css`) |
| Foreground | `#f5f5f7` | Body text |
| Accent | `#e8390d` | CTAs, links, highlights, icons |
| Muted | `zinc-400` / `slate-900` | Secondary text, borders, cards |

Use the accent sparingly — hover states, key actions, and emphasis only.

## Typography

- **Body/UI**: `poppins` from `@/app/font` (applied in root layout)
- **Blog/code**: `jetbrainsMono` — apply via `className={jetbrainsMono.className}` on blog pages

## Motion & Accessibility

- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` for Framer Motion and scroll effects
- Keep animations subtle; stagger hero reveals, avoid blocking first paint
- Include meaningful `alt` text and `aria-*` where interactive
- Skip-to-content link exists in layout — preserve it when editing `layout.tsx`

## Layout

- Mobile-first Tailwind breakpoints (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`)
- Portfolio sections: `max-w-7xl` containers, generous vertical padding
- Blog articles: `max-w-4xl` prose width
